dct_title_s: Gts. d'urbanisme du bassin houiller du Pas-de-Calais : plan topographique
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contour interval and spot heights. "Coordonnées Lambert I." "Dessine en 1955 a l'aide du 1/20.000 e. de l'I.G.N." Coverage complete in 17 sheets. Sheets are numbered through 16 including 1bis. Map collection has only 1: Groupt d'Auchel-Bruay. Sheet 1-bis of 17.
dct_creator_sm: France. Ministère de la reconstruction et du logement
dct_publisher_sm: Paris : Ministere de la reconstruction et du logement, 1955.
